  #------- MEDIAN INCOME -------#

  ### NEW BLOCK ###
  blocks {
    title: "Median Income"
    description: "Income and the cost of living can help us understand where and how food insecurity impacts communities at the local level. Often, communities with higher costs of living have a segment of the population living below the poverty line with low access to balanced, nutritional meals."
