  #------- FARM PRODUCTION -------#

  ### NEW BLOCK ###
  blocks {
    title: "Farm Production"
    description: "Irrigation and depleting water sources play an increasingly critical role on farms. Crops vary in their dependence on irrigation, with many vegetables and more sensitive grains being completely reliant on supplementary water to survive harsh summers. Other crops require supplemental water from irrigation to be economically viable, but are unlikely to die or completely fail without it.\n\nWith climate change impacting access to reliable irrigation, how will farmers need to adapt to this depleting resource? "
